data.description: REDUCED!!! This is a BEAUTIFUL 4 BEDROOM / 2.5 BATH Home with plenty of space and a GREAT floorplan. In addition, this Home also has a 580 SF bonus room! To top it off, there is a 20x24 shop that is included on this spacious 3.48 acre lot. This AWESOME Home has new interior re-paint in the main living and play areas. Also, there is wiring for a separate electric charging station to be installed for Electrical Vehicles in the Garage, with SOLAR PANELS on the Roof! Very affordable utility bills!  This lovely property is conveniently located off of Sunny Gap, allowing quick access to Conway, Greenbrier and Vilonia. You will not be disappointed!!! Lotos of outside lanscaping with a LARGE Covered Patio with a built in grill, firepit, extra seating, and a tree house. AGENTS PLEASEE CONFIDENTIAL REMARKS FOR SOME ADDITIONAL INFORMATION.
